<h1><span id="Indian_Defence">Indian Defence</span></h1>
<h3><span id="2._Nf3">2. Nf3</span></h3>
<p>White develops a piece to its ideal square and keeps his options open.  This move also is important for controlling the center.
</p><p>This position is also often reached via the move order 1.Nf3 Nf6 2.d4
</p>
<p><b>1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3</b>
</p>
